        "Run-On Sentence Detection: Identifies and helps break up long, structurally flawed sentences.",
        "Real-Time Feedback: See suggestions highlighted as you type or paste.",
        "Educational Explanations: Hover over a correction to see a brief explanation of the grammar rule.",
        "Free Web-Based Interface: No downloads, plugins, or extensions required."
